<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mljạ̉ wqwẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 mal̊jāuⁿ̉ waqūãẗuⁿ ʿaẘnaⁿạ fī ạlḍĩẙqāti wujida sẖadīdaⁿạ ạallhu lanā
 lidẖlika lạa nakẖ̊sẖay̱ walaẘ tazaḥ̊zaḥati ạlạảr̊ḍu wān̊qalabati ạl̊jibālu ại̹lay̱ qal̊bi ạl̊biḥāri
 nah̊ruⁿ sawāqīhi tufarĩḥu madīnaẗa ạllh ạllhu fī wasaṭihā falan̊ tatazaʿ̊zaʿa
 ʿajãti ạlạủmamu tazaʿ̊zaʿati ạl̊mamāliku ạảʿ̊ṭay̱ ṣaẘtahu dẖābati ạlạảr̊ḍu
 halumũwạ ạn̊ẓurūạ ạảʿ̊māla ạllh i kaẙfa jaʿala kẖirabaⁿạ fī ạlạảr̊ḍi
 musakĩnu ạlḥurūbi ại̹lay̱ ạảq̊ṣay̱ ạlạảr̊ḍi yak̊siru ạl̊qaẘsa wayaq̊ṭaʿu ạlrũm̊ḥa
 kufũwạ wāʿ̊lamūạ ạảnĩy ạảnā ạllhu: ạảtaʿālay̱ baẙna ạlạủmami ạảtaʿālay̱ fī ạlạảr̊ḍi
 rabũ ạl̊junūdi maʿanā mal̊jāủnā ại̹lhu yaʿ̊qūba
 yā jamīʿa ạlạủmami ṣafĩqūạ biạlạảyādī ạh̊tifūạ illhi biṣaẘti ạlạb̊tihāji
 lạảnã ạlrãbã ʿalīuⁿ̃ makẖūfuⁿ hūa, malikuⁿ kabīruⁿ ʿalay̱ kulĩ ạlạảr̊ḍi</lyrics>
<author>ktạbyẗ, mạjd ʿạdl</author>
<hymn_number>6742</hymn_number>
</song>